WEBVTT

00:00.125 --> 00:01.875
Anna has three siblings.

00:02.625 --> 00:06.625
Her older brother is already doing an apprenticeship in a
 carpentry workshop.

00:07.125 --> 00:11.375
Her two younger siblings are 4 and 6 years old.

00:11.625 --> 00:14.875
When her father comes home tired from
 work in the evening

00:14.900 --> 00:16.600
and the little ones are running around,

00:16.650 --> 00:20.125
he shouts a lot and 
 sometimes beats up the children.

00:21.125 --> 00:23.375
Anna and her mother then try to arbitrate.

00:24.125 --> 00:26.375
But they often lack the energy to do so.
